			[PLACEHOLDER: one-paragraph introduction to the capabilities offered]
		</p>
	</div>

	<section class="capability reveal">
		<h2 class="capability-title tick">[PLACEHOLDER: capability one]</h2>
		<p>[PLACEHOLDER: description of capability one]</p>
	</section>

	<section class="capability reveal">
		<h2 class="capability-title tick">[PLACEHOLDER: capability two]</h2>
		<p>[PLACEHOLDER: description of capability two]</p>
	</section>

	<section class="capability reveal">
		<h2 class="capability-title tick">[PLACEHOLDER: capability three]</h2>
		<p>[PLACEHOLDER: description of capability three]</p>
	</section>
</Base>
